  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THE DEFINITIVE ARCADE RACER FOR VR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through neon cities, alien worlds, and orbital circuits. Lean into every turn using intuitive chest-based controls designed for comfort and immersion. Outrun missiles, drop mines, and blast your way to victory—this is VR racing at full throttle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/c13d997f43a0542876ce522c5911c524.poster.avif?t=1762447646\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/c13d997f43a0542876ce522c5911c524.webm?t=1762447646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/c13d997f43a0542876ce522c5911c524.mp4?t=1762447646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏁 SEVEN GAME MODES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo, competitive, or chaotic—choose from Time Trial, Weekly Challenge, Combat, Survivor, Neon Runner, Multiplayer, and Career.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/8452e7a0353e9efdbd698c36f35e84c1.poster.avif?t=1762447646\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/8452e7a0353e9efdbd698c36f35e84c1.webm?t=1762447646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/8452e7a0353e9efdbd698c36f35e84c1.mp4?t=1762447646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌐 MULTIPLAYER & SOCIAL HUB</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race with up to 6 players in cross-platform online multiplayer. Choose your avatar and meet up in a social lobby between sessions. ‎</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/b8de7fbf45f0ecb851e222205cd9ce50.poster.avif?t=1762447646\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/b8de7fbf45f0ecb851e222205cd9ce50.webm?t=1762447646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/b8de7fbf45f0ecb851e222205cd9ce50.mp4?t=1762447646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>🌌 30 TRACKS ACROSS THE GALAXY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >‎ Race through highland valleys, desert colonies, neon-lit cities, and orbital spaceways. Each circuit offers unique challenges, visual styles, and hazards to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/bd3b00ae7da9cef417d5c0b825dea898.poster.avif?t=1762447646\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/bd3b00ae7da9cef417d5c0b825dea898.webm?t=1762447646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/bd3b00ae7da9cef417d5c0b825dea898.mp4?t=1762447646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💥 COMBAT RACING</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use missiles, drones, EMPs, and more in fast-paced battles where every second counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/4f5232b1dcb367a2efcbcb1b86475682.poster.avif?t=1762447646\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/4f5232b1dcb367a2efcbcb1b86475682.webm?t=1762447646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/4f5232b1dcb367a2efcbcb1b86475682.mp4?t=1762447646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎨 LIVERY EDITOR &  SHOWROOM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design custom bikes, suits, and helmets in full VR.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>📸 PHOTO & REPLAY TOOLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pause time mid-race, fly through your replay, and capture your best moments from any angle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/668430/extras/f134fec42a84fafb81da32efa00319ca.avif?t=1762447646\" width=800 height=450 /></span>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
